Alexis Loret https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alexis_Loret 0 Alexis Loret (born 10 January 1975) is a French film and television actor. Devoting himself initially to cabinetmaking, he became a model, and was noticed by André Téchiné. Alexis_Loret ( born_10_January_1975 ) is a_French_film_and_television_actor .
